title: Kings of Leon - B-Sides and Rarities Vol. 1-4
description:
The following is a four volume collection of 44 songs. Collecting these tracks was very time consuming and as a gift to fellow fans I have bundled them together to save you guys/gals the headache of finding them. All tracks are tagged and include artwork. There will be more to come, but for the foreseeable future this is it. 

A big thanks to [size=4]coombeh[/size] for contributing greatly to volume 4!

===================================================
